    "en": {
      "title": "First death from monkey measles recorded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "India's first death due to monkeypox, known as monkeypox.",
        "In this, a 22-year-old youth, who had entered Kerala's Thrissur area from the United Arab Kingdom, died on Saturday after being admitted to the hospital due to symptoms.",
        "The Kerala Health Minister has announced that a post-mortem examination has confirmed that he was infected with monkey measles. (R)"
      ],
